Of course I am.

275
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:52,226
Emotionally, yes.

276
00:16:52,226 --> 00:16:55,386
But legally, the evidence is insufficient.

277
00:16:55,386 --> 00:16:56,440
He held her hand.

278
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:59,400
Is that not enough to call it cheating?

279
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:01,480
It doesn't count as solid evidence.

280
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:03,000
But,

281
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:05,579
you have the right to break up with him.

282
00:17:07,120 --> 00:17:08,840
Me, break up with him?

283
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:10,553
Yes.

284
00:17:13,120 --> 00:17:14,799
Lawyer Xu, you've got it wrong.

285
00:17:14,799 --> 00:17:17,780
That guy is my best friend's boyfriend.

286
00:17:26,080 --> 00:17:29,120
Sorry, my mistake.

287
00:17:29,120 --> 00:17:30,240
It's okay.

288
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:32,946
I'm just torn about
whether to send her the photo or not.

289
00:17:32,946 --> 00:17:34,599
What if I send it to her

290
00:17:34,599 --> 00:17:35,790
and it turns out I was wrong?

291
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:37,493
Wouldn't that just be causing drama?

292
00:17:37,493 --> 00:17:39,080
But if he really is a jerk, cheating--

293
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:41,960
If they are truly in love,

294
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:45,280
they won't split just because you sent a photo.

295
00:17:45,280 --> 00:17:47,520
If they already have trust issues,

296
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:49,475
even if you don't send this photo,

297
00:17:49,475 --> 00:17:50,759
their relationship

298
00:17:50,759 --> 00:17:53,360
will come to an end sooner or later.

299
00:17:54,260 --> 00:17:56,426
That makes sense.

300
00:17:56,426 --> 00:17:57,440
Lawyer Xu,

301
00:17:57,440 --> 00:18:00,526
you seem to have quite a lot of insight
and experience in relationships.

302
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:13,039
Lawyer Xu,

303
00:18:13,039 --> 00:18:15,579
that's not what I meant.

304
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:23,880
While abroad, I handled some divorce cases.

305
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:25,600
When you see enough of them,

306
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:28,240
you naturally gain more experience.

307
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:31,500
I see.

308
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:35,586
What I said might not be right.

309
00:18:35,586 --> 00:18:37,040
Think it over yourself

310
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:39,280
before making a decision.

311
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:43,580
Thank you, Lawyer Xu.

312
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:25,920
[Volume Down]

313
00:22:03,599 --> 00:22:05,279
I'm so sorry, Lawyer Xu.

314
00:22:05,279 --> 00:22:07,960
I accidentally fell asleep.

315
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:10,273
When did we arrive?

316
00:22:10,273 --> 00:22:11,440
Just now.

317
00:22:11,440 --> 00:22:13,653
I was just about to wake you.

318
00:22:15,359 --> 00:22:17,560
Thank you for driving me back.

319
00:22:17,560 --> 00:22:19,380
You're welcome.

320
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,440
I'll get going now.

321
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:39,120
Drive safely, Lawyer Xu.

322
00:22:39,120 --> 00:22:40,279
Yes.

323
00:22:40,279 --> 00:22:41,993
- Goodbye.
- Okay.

324
00:23:05,800 --> 00:23:07,880
Ming Ying, what's up?

325
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,353
<i>Hey, Ruan Yu. Do you have a minute?</i>

326
00:23:09,353 --> 00:23:11,553
<i>I have something to tell you.</i>

327
00:23:12,920 --> 00:23:15,400
I actually have something to tell you, too.

328
00:23:15,400 --> 00:23:17,480
You go first.

329
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:18,920
I noticed that a lot of Cen Si Si's

330
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:21,840
photos on social media are imitating yours.

331
00:23:21,840 --> 00:23:24,333
You wanted to tell me about Cen Si Si?

332
00:23:24,333 --> 00:23:26,540
Yeah, what's wrong?

333
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:31,559
Nothing else to say?

334
00:23:31,559 --> 00:23:33,400
You mean the thing with Zhang Chuan?

335
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,759
He told me as soon as he got home.

336
00:23:34,759 --> 00:23:36,599
He said that,
today he dined with a female client,

337
00:23:36,599 --> 00:23:37,799
and you happened to see them.

338
00:23:37,799 --> 00:23:39,240
It was just a misunderstanding.

339
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:41,559
It's fine. That deal's dead. Whatever.

340
00:23:41,559 --> 00:23:43,440
He can just find another one.

341
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:45,359
So he just told you

342
00:23:45,359 --> 00:23:47,120
he was dining with a female client?

343
00:23:47,120 --> 00:23:48,246
Yeah.

344
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:51,280
What's wrong?

345
00:23:51,280 --> 00:23:53,540
What else did you see?

346
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:11,720
Look at this.

347
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,119
He told me about this, too.

348
00:24:13,119 --> 00:24:15,440
The product they were testing today
was a hand cream.

349
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,880
They were just testing the product.

350
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,320
But you saw them,

351
00:24:18,320 --> 00:24:21,173
and thought he was holding her hand.

352
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:24,840
He was just applying hand cream.

353
00:24:24,840 --> 00:24:27,380
Oh, maybe I was wrong.

354
00:24:28,119 --> 00:24:29,319
Don't worry.

355
00:24:29,319 --> 00:24:31,520
If he ever actually dares to cheat,
you won't have to tell me.

356
00:24:31,520 --> 00:24:33,366
I'll dump him immediately.

357
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:37,000
- Alright.
- Just keep an eye out. I'm hanging up.

358
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:38,760
<i>Bye!</i>

359
00:24:38,760 --> 00:24:40,240
From now on, let someone else

360
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:41,480
handle the offline coordination.

361
00:24:41,480 --> 00:24:43,359
I'll only be responsible
for remote product testing

362
00:24:43,359 --> 00:24:44,520
and livestream promotions.

363
00:24:44,520 --> 00:24:46,000
<i>I just thought that face of yours</i>

364
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:48,160
<i>would work on those female clients.</i>

365
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:50,839
<i>You're wasting your edge by acting like this.</i>

366
00:24:50,839 --> 00:24:53,559
<i>It's just playing along.
It's not like you're cheating.</i>

367
00:24:53,559 --> 00:24:55,039
<i>How will you make money being so rigid?</i>

368
00:24:55,039 --> 00:24:56,920
<i>Don't regret it
when your girlfriend dumps you broke.</i>

369
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:58,773
That's just your opinion!

370
00:24:58,773 --> 00:25:00,360
My girlfriend and I are doing great!

371
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:02,113
You don't need to worry about us!

372
00:25:10,080 --> 00:25:12,380
Are you done soaking, babe?

373
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:16,839
The water's gone cold.

374
00:25:16,839 --> 00:25:21,000
I told you,
soaking for too long isn't good for you.

375
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:23,080
Why has this thing been auto-shutting lately?

376
00:25:23,080 --> 00:25:25,120
I wasn't paying attention.

377
00:25:26,560 --> 00:25:29,170
I got you some new saffron soak packets.
Coming tomorrow.

378
00:25:29,170 --> 00:25:30,440
Really? That's great.

379
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:33,319
I'm already tired of using these mugwort ones.

380
00:25:33,319 --> 00:25:35,220
Here.

381
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:38,180
Go pour it out.

382
00:26:15,360 --> 00:26:18,100
Babe, have you seen my phone? I just...

383
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:24,279
Why can't you break
that forgetful habit of yours?

384
00:26:24,279 --> 00:26:25,436
Well, I have you, don't I?

385
00:26:25,436 --> 00:26:27,000
Yeah.

386
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:42,000
The fried chicken is almost here.

387
00:26:42,000 --> 00:26:43,200
Ruan Yu is almost here, too.

388
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:45,440
Get ready, okay?

389
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:47,760
It's only eleven. Isn't she arriving at noon?

390
00:26:47,760 --> 00:26:49,400
She's afraid of missing the best time

391
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:50,440
to make the phone call.

392
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:53,540
That's why she left an hour early.

393
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:03,833
Why aren't you picking up?

394
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:06,599
- Hello!
- Hello!

395
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:09,680
Excuse me. Is Zhikun Law Firm right here?

396
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:11,560
Yes, it is.

397
00:27:11,560 --> 00:27:13,200
This is for someone called

398
00:27:13,200 --> 00:27:15,200
Xu Huai...

399
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:17,220
It's a food delivery.

400
00:27:18,079 --> 00:27:19,080
Excuse me.

401
00:27:19,080 --> 00:27:21,440
Is this a delivery for Xu Huai Song?

402
00:27:21,440 --> 00:27:22,706
I think so.

403
00:27:22,706 --> 00:27:24,440
Give it to me. I'll take it up for you.

404
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:26,720
Thanks for the help.

405
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:32,220
Pick up the phone!

406
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:40,600
Lawyer Xu,

407
00:27:40,600 --> 00:27:42,400
your delivery's here.

408
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:45,040
Delivery? I didn't order anything.

409
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:48,141
Your name is on it.

410
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:50,720
Then it must be a mistake.

411
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:52,080
I never eat takeout.

412
00:27:52,080 --> 00:27:54,953
Besides, I don't have any
local food delivery apps.

413
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:57,359
There you are.

414
00:27:57,359 --> 00:27:59,400
Ruan Yu, you're here.

415
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:00,759
Where's your fried chicken?

416
00:28:00,759 --> 00:28:02,560
I got you a Coke. It's already downstairs.

417
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:04,880
Coke and fried chicken. A perfect match, buddy.

418
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,960
Where's the fried chicken?

419
00:28:07,799 --> 00:28:09,200
Right here.

420
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:10,480
You brought it up?

421
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:12,940
Perfect. Let's eat together then.

422
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,750
<i>Song, listen!</i>

423
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:21,240
<i>Ruan Yu might not</i>

424
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:23,359
<i>even like you anymore.</i>

425
00:28:23,359 --> 00:28:24,960
<i>Even if she still feels something,</i>

426
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:26,039
<i>the person in her heart</i>

427
00:28:26,039 --> 00:28:29,200
<i>isn't the real you at all.</i>

428
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,319
<i>She doesn't even know</i>

429
00:28:30,319 --> 00:28:32,960
<i>that you love fried chicken.</i>

430
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:34,760
<i>If you come clean,</i>

431
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:37,013
<i>will she accept the real you?</i>

432
00:28:38,080 --> 00:28:40,080
Lawyer Liu recently joined a weight loss

433
00:28:40,080 --> 00:28:42,680
group with his colleagues.

434
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:45,039
If anyone gets caught ordering takeout,

435
00:28:45,039 --> 00:28:48,319
they have to send a red packet
in the company group chat.

436
00:28:48,319 --> 00:28:49,720
But it's okay, Lawyer Liu.

437
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:51,640
If you want to order it again,

438
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:53,973
you can still use my name.

439
00:28:53,973 --> 00:28:56,800
I'll cover for you.

440
00:28:56,800 --> 00:28:58,720
But just so you know,

441
00:28:58,720 --> 00:29:01,346
fried chicken is really unhealthy.

442
00:29:01,346 --> 00:29:03,573
You should eat less of it.

443
00:29:05,600 --> 00:29:07,096
Got it. Alright,

444
00:29:07,096 --> 00:29:08,760
I understand.

445
00:29:08,760 --> 00:29:10,440
Well, Lawyer Xu,

446
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:11,799
you stay disciplined.

447
00:29:11,799 --> 00:29:13,320
- Of course.
- Alright then.

448
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:16,320
Here, Ruan Yu. Let me pour you some Coke.

449
00:29:16,320 --> 00:29:18,920
Coke and fried chicken.

450
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:20,560
Perfect!

451
00:29:20,560 --> 00:29:22,520
Thank you!

452
00:29:22,520 --> 00:29:24,519
Lawyer Xu, no Coke for you either.

453
00:29:24,519 --> 00:29:26,700
Coke is just as unhealthy.

454
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:37,059
This is delicious.

455
00:29:48,040 --> 00:29:50,620
<i>Smells amazing!</i>

456
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:57,720
<i>Ming Ying, you want a drumstick, right?</i>

457
00:29:57,720 --> 00:29:59,119
<i>You take it.</i>

458
00:29:59,119 --> 00:30:01,280
<i>Didn't you just say
you were so hungry you could eat two?</i>

459
00:30:01,280 --> 00:30:03,520
<i>I want stir-fried cucumber and eggs.</i>

460
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:05,760
<i>I'll just eat this.</i>

461
00:30:08,839 --> 00:30:11,020
<i>Give me a drumstick.</i>

462
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,480
<i>A drumstick is what I desire,</i>

463
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:19,000
<i>and Xu Huai Song is also what I desire.</i>

464
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:20,520
<i>But I cannot have both.</i>

465
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:23,606
<i>So I'll give up the drumstick for Xu Huai Song.</i>

466
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:26,529
<i>You're really not eating?</i>

467
00:30:26,529 --> 00:30:27,600
<i>I don't like it.</i>

468
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:30,240
<i>Then it's mine.</i>

469
00:30:40,760 --> 00:30:42,559
I actually ate before I left,

470
00:30:42,559 --> 00:30:43,840
so I'm not hungry.

471
00:30:43,840 --> 00:30:46,600
Lawyer Liu, you go ahead and eat.

472
00:30:46,600 --> 00:30:47,920
You're not eating either?

473
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:49,799
Then, Ruan Yu,

474
00:30:49,799 --> 00:30:52,339
have this drink.

475
00:30:53,079 --> 00:30:55,079
It's good.

476
00:30:55,079 --> 00:30:56,320
Lawyer Xu.

477
00:30:56,320 --> 00:30:57,680
Have a drink.

478
00:30:57,680 --> 00:30:58,920
I think you'll like this one.

479
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:00,240
It's healthier too.

480
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:01,833
Thanks.

481
00:31:03,280 --> 00:31:06,720
A cup of pure black coffee for you.

482
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:10,666
Wishing you an energetic day!

483
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:25,920
Last time, Lawyer Xu

484
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:28,359
drank coffee like it were Coke.

485
00:31:28,359 --> 00:31:30,440
Isn't it bitter?

486
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:32,300
My habit.

487
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:43,720
<i>Lawyer Xu, are you drinking...</i>

488
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:45,170
<i>black coffee?</i>

489
00:31:45,170 --> 00:31:47,080
<i>It's the first time I've seen</i>

490
00:31:47,080 --> 00:31:49,600
<i>someone gulp black coffee.</i>

491
00:31:49,600 --> 00:31:51,240
<i>Yes.</i>

492
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:53,139
<i>My habit.</i>

493
00:31:58,000 --> 00:32:00,040
Well, for some things,

494
00:32:00,040 --> 00:32:02,520
only you know

495
00:32:02,520 --> 00:32:04,993
if they're bitter or not.

496
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:09,466
Right, Lawyer Xu?

497
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,533
This is delicious.

498
00:32:20,600 --> 00:32:22,539
I'm making the call now.

499
00:32:34,040 --> 00:32:35,833
[Cen Si Si]

500
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,680
Hello, this is Ruan Yu.

501
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:40,680
Is this Cen Si Si?

502
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:42,200
<i>Yes, it's me.</i>

503
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:44,079
<i>I've saved your number.</i>

504
00:32:44,079 --> 00:32:45,820
Identity confirmed.

505
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:50,120
Is it a good time to talk?

506
00:32:50,120 --> 00:32:51,926
<i>Yes, go ahead.</i>

507
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:53,880
Here's the thing.

508
00:32:53,880 --> 00:32:55,400
I was planning to have my lawyer

509
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:57,464
handle the settlement talks.

510
00:32:57,464 --> 00:32:58,840
But I changed my mind.

511
00:32:58,840 --> 00:33:01,360
I think it's better if we talk first.

512
00:33:01,360 --> 00:33:02,760
Actually, a film company

513
00:33:02,760 --> 00:33:06,426
reached out to me a while back
about an adaptation.

514
00:33:16,866 --> 00:33:18,079
Here's the deal.

515
00:33:18,079 --> 00:33:19,160
They want me to

516
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:21,079
properly handle this scandal.

517
00:33:21,079 --> 00:33:22,080
Otherwise,

518
00:33:22,080 --> 00:33:24,360
the film adaptation will fall through.

519
00:33:24,360 --> 00:33:26,966
Senior, the signal's bad here.

520
00:33:26,966 --> 00:33:28,920
Why don't we talk in person?

521
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:31,759
How about we meet
at Nanhu Restaurant at 1:00 PM?

522
00:33:31,759 --> 00:33:34,359
It's pretty close to your place.

523
00:33:34,359 --> 00:33:37,059
Okay, see you then.

524
00:33:39,759 --> 00:33:41,640
She seems to be on guard.

525
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:43,119
From here to Nanhu Restaurant,

526
00:33:43,119 --> 00:33:45,079
it takes about 20 minutes.

527
00:33:45,079 --> 00:33:47,319
I'll head over now
to make sure nothing goes wrong.

528
00:33:47,319 --> 00:33:49,419
Can you handle it alone?

529
00:33:50,799 --> 00:33:53,099
Should be fine.

530
00:33:55,960 --> 00:33:58,480
We only have one shot at this.

531
00:33:58,480 --> 00:34:00,379
I'll go with you.

532
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:10,840
The voice recorder.

533
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:12,039
Push up to record.

534
00:34:12,039 --> 00:34:14,060
Push down to save.

535
00:34:33,079 --> 00:34:35,260
Thank you, Lawyer Xu.

536
00:35:05,640 --> 00:35:07,719
I thought getting her to talk over the phone

537
00:35:07,719 --> 00:35:09,400
wouldn't be that hard.

538
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:11,560
But now that we're actually meeting,

539
00:35:12,240 --> 00:35:14,346
my heart is racing.

540
00:35:20,120 --> 00:35:22,581
Do some eye exercises.

541
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:28,360
You wrote about it in your novel.

542
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:30,400
It seemed to work.

543
00:35:59,520 --> 00:36:00,709
<i>Sorry,</i>

544
00:36:00,709 --> 00:36:02,320
<i>I held the wrong hand.</i>

545
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:04,486
<i>Wrong hand?</i>

546
00:36:05,480 --> 00:36:06,960
<i>Then...</i>

547
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:09,413
<i>Who is the right person?</i>

548
00:36:14,519 --> 00:36:16,459
<i>Jerk!</i>

549
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:22,880
Just a novel.

550
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:25,020
It's all fake.

551
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:31,160
<i>So was the eye exercise thing fake?</i>

552
00:36:31,160 --> 00:36:34,600
<i>Or was liking me fake?</i>

553
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:41,400
<i>What's the use of eye exercises?</i>

554
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:44,480
<i>That day, I just called him a jerk
a hundred times</i>

555
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:47,700
<i>till I calmed down and fell asleep.</i>

556
00:37:07,599 --> 00:37:09,239
Senior,

557
00:37:09,239 --> 00:37:10,920
thanks for giving me this chance

558
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:13,246
to explain to you in person.

559
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:16,009
Si Si,

560
00:37:16,009 --> 00:37:18,239
I've thought it over.

561
00:37:18,239 --> 00:37:20,660
Settlement is fine.

562
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:23,240
But my lawyer

563
00:37:23,240 --> 00:37:24,880
doesn't just represent me.

564
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:27,159
He also has to consider the film company.

565
00:37:27,159 --> 00:37:28,240
In order not to affect

566
00:37:28,240 --> 00:37:30,480
the adaptation of the novel,

567
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:33,560
they require that in your apologetic statement,

568
00:37:33,560 --> 00:37:36,560
you admit that you both posted
that defamatory Weibo,

569
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:39,160
and sent trolls after me.

570
00:37:39,160 --> 00:37:40,546
I...

571
00:37:40,546 --> 00:37:42,513
I didn't do that!

572
00:37:45,240 --> 00:37:48,819
I know that issuing such a statement
would be really hard on you.

573
00:37:49,440 --> 00:37:51,560
But the film company's position is that

574
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:54,320
if we can't settle, we go to court.

575
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:55,960
Senior,

576
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:58,079
I...

577
00:37:58,079 --> 00:38:01,400
I really didn't mean it.

578
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:03,760
When I posted that thread,

579
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:06,840
I genuinely believed it.

580
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:09,519
I didn't know back then
that you were Wen Xiang.

581
00:38:09,519 --> 00:38:12,480
And that thread going viral later.

582
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:14,120
That wasn't me.

583
00:38:14,120 --> 00:38:17,120
That was just the netizens' own doing.

584
00:38:19,079 --> 00:38:20,680
Si Si.

585
00:38:20,680 --> 00:38:22,560
The Internet is not a lawless place.

586
00:38:22,560 --> 00:38:25,120
Everything leaves a trace.

587
00:38:25,120 --> 00:38:26,880
Even if you deny it now,

588
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:28,053
once the investigation begins,

589
00:38:28,053 --> 00:38:30,260
it will come out.

590
00:38:31,640 --> 00:38:34,560
After all, we went to the same school.

591
00:38:34,560 --> 00:38:36,353
You're my junior.

592
00:38:37,240 --> 00:38:39,559
Of course, I don't want things

593
00:38:39,559 --> 00:38:41,546
to get too ugly.

594
00:38:42,560 --> 00:38:44,360
Then...

595
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:47,440
Then, Senior...

596
00:38:47,440 --> 00:38:50,360
can you drop the case first?

597
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:52,199
You can still

598
00:38:52,199 --> 00:38:55,079
have your lawyer look into everything after.

599
00:38:55,079 --> 00:38:56,199
We settle out of court.

600
00:38:56,199 --> 00:38:57,480
Nice and peaceful.

601
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:59,819
Wouldn't that be great?

602
00:39:02,079 --> 00:39:05,120
That's not a bad idea.

603
00:39:05,120 --> 00:39:07,039
But what if I drop the case,

604
00:39:07,039 --> 00:39:08,680
and someone with bad intentions

605
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:11,160
twists it into me being guilty,

606
00:39:11,160 --> 00:39:13,433
then gets the Poet to sue me?

607
00:39:13,433 --> 00:39:15,780
What would I do then?

608
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:20,180
Senior, aren't you overthinking it?

609
00:39:32,120 --> 00:39:33,800
<i>If the conversation hits a dead end,</i>

610
00:39:33,800 --> 00:39:35,880
<i>break away from your original logic.</i>

611
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:38,280
<i>Try changing the subject, stir her emotions</i>

612
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:40,740
<i>to make her let her guard down.</i>

613
00:39:51,159 --> 00:39:53,019
Si Si,

614
00:39:56,719 --> 00:39:58,420
to be honest,

615
00:39:59,160 --> 00:40:01,740
I've been having a hard time lately.

616
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:06,078
I know

617
00:40:06,078 --> 00:40:08,659
that in this situation,

618
00:40:09,640 --> 00:40:12,105
forget selling the film rights.

619
00:40:12,105 --> 00:40:14,039
If this keeps up, the platform

620
00:40:14,039 --> 00:40:16,860
could drop me at any moment.

621
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:22,039
How could that be, Senior?

622
00:40:22,039 --> 00:40:24,720
You're the platform's cash cow.

623
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:28,212
New authors pop up all the time.

624
00:40:28,212 --> 00:40:31,000
Once I'm kicked out of Qianhe Net,

625
00:40:31,000 --> 00:40:34,261
no other platform will want to sign me.

626
00:40:37,520 --> 00:40:39,720
You're worrying too much.

627
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:41,280
Even if that day comes,

628
00:40:41,280 --> 00:40:44,676
at least Shi Can won't just sit back and watch.

629
00:40:44,676 --> 00:40:46,200
After all, back in school,

630
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:47,880
you looked out for him.

631
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:49,480
Right?

632
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:51,599
He's so busy now.

633
00:40:51,599 --> 00:40:54,419
He won't have time for such trifles.

634
00:40:56,680 --> 00:40:58,920
I was thinking,

635
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:02,920
if it really was you behind the trolls,

636
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:05,552
at least with Shi Can as the connection,

637
00:41:05,552 --> 00:41:08,253
I could still beg you to stop.

638
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:16,846
In that case,

639
00:41:18,639 --> 00:41:21,180
why not just beg me, Senior?

640
00:41:26,039 --> 00:41:28,260
It really was you!

641
00:41:30,520 --> 00:41:33,720
You knew all along that I was Wen Xiang!

642
00:41:34,640 --> 00:41:36,040
Even if I said I didn't know,

643
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:38,440
you never believed me anyway.

644
00:41:40,480 --> 00:41:43,360
Didn't you tell me that in college,

645
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:45,320
you decided to become a writer
because you saw my work

646
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:47,193
in a magazine?

647
00:41:48,360 --> 00:41:51,120
You're thinking way too highly of yourself.

648
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:55,180
You've been plagiarizing since then, right?

649
00:42:01,119 --> 00:42:02,920
Why should a plagiarized story

650
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:05,720
get such good stats?

651
00:42:05,720 --> 00:42:09,119
I just wanted everyone to see the truth.

652
00:42:09,119 --> 00:42:10,679
I just didn't expect you

653
00:42:10,679 --> 00:42:13,700
to be so fragile, Ruan Yu.

654
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:20,140
I only hired a few trolls,

655
00:42:20,920 --> 00:42:22,899
and you're already...

656
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:27,379
falling apart.

657
00:42:33,159 --> 00:42:36,060
- Come down!
- Come catch me!

658
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:40,440
I'm sorry, miss!

659
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:17,079
Having fun with the phone?

660
00:43:17,079 --> 00:43:18,200
Yeah.

661
00:43:18,200 --> 00:43:21,000
You never played with it before?

662
00:43:21,760 --> 00:43:23,899
Let me try it for a bit.

663
00:43:31,480 --> 00:43:33,519
Caught red-handed.

664
00:43:33,519 --> 00:43:37,100
No use denying it. Hand it over.

665
00:43:45,480 --> 00:43:47,159
Dean Zhu!

666
00:43:47,159 --> 00:43:49,440
Xu Huai Shi!

667
00:43:49,440 --> 00:43:51,600
You've gone too far!

668
00:43:52,400 --> 00:43:53,639
You're such a real "loyal" friend.

669
00:43:53,639 --> 00:43:56,140
You gave my phone to the teacher!

670
00:43:57,360 --> 00:43:59,960
So this phone is yours?

671
00:43:59,960 --> 00:44:02,000
Yes. I don't hide from who I am.

672
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:04,480
It's mine.

673
00:44:04,480 --> 00:44:06,440
So this is what you're into?

674
00:44:06,440 --> 00:44:09,206
A male celebrity winking at you?

675
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:12,259
No laughing!

676
00:44:18,440 --> 00:44:20,819
That's my freedom.

677
00:44:22,320 --> 00:44:24,079
Freedom, huh?

678
00:44:24,079 --> 00:44:26,060
There are words here, too.

679
00:44:27,159 --> 00:44:28,519
"Shi Can, Shi Can,

680
00:44:28,519 --> 00:44:29,760
my love will never change."

681
00:44:29,760 --> 00:44:32,019
That your freedom, too?

682
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:37,119
I...

683
00:44:37,119 --> 00:44:38,800
wrote this too.

684
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:40,119
Okay!

685
00:44:40,119 --> 00:44:41,600
You wrote this, too.

686
00:44:41,600 --> 00:44:43,840
Then I'm curious.

687
00:44:43,840 --> 00:44:45,680
Why is your phone's wallpaper

688
00:44:45,680 --> 00:44:48,800
a picture of her with a male celebrity?

689
00:44:51,240 --> 00:44:53,280
What does this mean?

690
00:44:53,280 --> 00:44:55,080
I...

691
00:44:55,840 --> 00:44:57,280
I ship them as partners!

692
00:44:57,280 --> 00:44:59,079
So you'll just play along with anything, huh?

693
00:44:59,079 --> 00:45:00,840
No laughing!

694
00:45:00,840 --> 00:45:02,679
Both of you, come to my office.

695
00:45:02,679 --> 00:45:03,760
No going home after school.

696
00:45:03,760 --> 00:45:04,960
Call your parents.

697
00:45:04,960 --> 00:45:06,960
<i>Please log in to your Huawei account.</i>

698
00:45:06,960 --> 00:45:09,060
What account?

699
00:45:16,559 --> 00:45:18,119
Thanks.

700
00:45:18,119 --> 00:45:19,719
For what?

701
00:45:19,719 --> 00:45:21,519
Didn't really help you though.

702
00:45:21,519 --> 00:45:23,080
That's not what I meant.

703
00:45:23,080 --> 00:45:25,120
Then what is it?

704
00:45:27,039 --> 00:45:28,360
I can't believe you said

705
00:45:28,360 --> 00:45:30,500
Li Shi Can and I are partners.

